channel.title: Basic sword
channel.description:
I decided to take my second model i made and edit it a bit. Now before you say it's 'flat', it doesn't matter if it is or isn't, what matters is what it looks like in game. and that's what this model is for.
I will add a in game picture when ever i get the time.
Meta: [img]http://img638.imageshack.us/img638/574/idksword333.png[/img] EDIT: i just noticed what the bottom of the sword looks like...:|
